h2 Usage

.uk-grid
  - 3.times do
    .uk-width-1-3
      .uk-panel.uk-panel-box
        code .uk-width-1-3

.uk-grid
  - 2.times do
    .uk-width-1-2
      .uk-panel.uk-panel-box
        code .uk-width-1-2

.uk-grid
  .uk-width-3-10
    .uk-panel.uk-panel-box
      code .uk-width-3-10
  .uk-width-7-10
    .uk-panel.uk-panel-box
      code .uk-width-7-10

